                     <interp inst="t18270531-304-person1664" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I secured them immediately.</p>
               <p>ASKIN's Defence. I was coming from the Docks - a man said, "Lay hold of this, I will pay you for your trouble."</p>
               <p>SKINNER's Defence. I was going to work.</p>
